snippet.title: ShowBiz Minute: Depp, 'American Crime Story,' Big Freedia
snippet.description:
Judge orders delay for Johnny Depp restraining order hearing; "American Crime Story" writers focusing on Hurricane Katrina; Bounce rapper Big Freedia's sentencing delayed until August 25. (Aug. 10)
